    <mj-section css-class="light-wrap">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text padding-top="0">
          <h1 style="color:#004C45;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin:0;text-align: left;"> A Message from Cal Poly Humboldt </h1>
          <p id="date" style="color:#004C45;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;margin:10px 0 20px 0;text-align: left;"> December 15, 2023 </p>
          <p style="color:#004C45;font-size:22px;font-weight:bold;margin:10px 0 20px 0; line-height:28px">Full Day off on Dec. 22 for Holiday Break</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-color="#F2A900" padding="0" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section css-class="light-wrap" padding-bottom="20px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text padding-bottom="0">Dear Colleagues,
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text>In celebration of the holiday season, Governor Newsom has authorized four hours of Informal Time Off (ITO) on Friday, Dec. 22, 2023. In addition, I have authorized an additional four hours of ITO. With that, the campus will be closed Dec. 22, 2023 through Jan. 1, 2024.</mj-text><mj-text>
          To maintain critical campus functions, some team members will work on Dec. 22. Employees who work may make arrangements with their supervisor for an alternative informal day off to be used before June 30, 2024.
      </mj-text><mj-text>
          Thank you for your many contributions in 2023. Relax and refresh. I look forward to working with you all in the new year.
      </mj-text><mj-text>
          Best wishes for a restful, healthy, and safe holiday season.
        </mj-text>


        <mj-image width="175px" align="left" src="https://mailings.humboldt.edu/general/signatures/presidentJackson_officialSignature-green.png" alt="President Jackson's signature" />
        <mj-text padding-top="0">
          <strong>Tom Jackson, Jr., President</strong><br />
          Cal Poly Humboldt</mj-text>

      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section padding="0 0 40px 0">
